    - control:
      + libdrm-intel1 Replaces libdrm2 (<= 2.4.1-0ubuntu5)
      + libdrm-dev depends on linux-libc-dev => 2.6.28-5.15 on
        [amd64 armel i386] only, and >= 2.6.28-2.4 on lpia
